      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered icon. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six features its signature 7,900-RPM redline and factory-spec individual throttle bodies, delivering linear power through a crisp 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis has been meticulously preserved, featuring a reinforced rear subframe and a fully overhauled VANOS system to ensure peak mechanical longevity. The variable M-differential remains tight, and the suspension retains its factory-correct geometry for telepathic steering response. Every seal is supple, the paint depth is uniform, and the interior shows zero bolster wear or pixel failure. A turn-key, investment-grade specimen with a comprehensive service dossier.",
